{"tid":2279650,"cid":5,"subCid":11,"title":"警長今年4月元朗聚餐時襲擊女同袍 判160小時社會服務令","createTime":"2020-11-10T02:39:49.000Z","updateTime":"2020-11-10T09:55:47.000Z","uid":240362,"like":4,"dislike":53,"uniUserReply":53,"replies":[{"pid":"6c9196e6846b6687929340fcb306c31923f96a02","tid":2279650,"uid":240362,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2020-11-10T02:39:49.000Z","msg":"10名警務人員於今年4月疑違反限聚令在元朗聚餐，期間1名男警長因不敬酒遭揶揄而起爭執，扯女同袍頭髮。被告早前承認1項普通襲擊罪，裁判官水佳麗今早在屯門裁判法院指被告身為警務人員，應樹立榜樣，遂接納報告建議，判處被告160小時社會服務令。<br />\n<br />\n40歲被告梁珏榮承認於今年4月19日在元朗屏會街13-17號屏會中心外行人路上，襲擊女子蘇伶雅。<br />\n<br />\n水官判刑時指整體報告意見良好，雖報告中列舉了家庭、壓力等多項因素致犯案，但歸根究底可說是因為「驕傲」，僅因紅酒潑濕皮鞋便發脾氣扯事主頭髮。而醫療報告指事主頭皮不只痛，還有腫脹，可見被告扯時不留手。水官遂依報告建議判處160小時社會服務令。"},{"pid":"0e6779c22faf7023bcdc1a9ffd3178e36f9a9767","tid":2279650,"uid":25858,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2020-11-10T02:40:49.000Z","msg":"<img src=\"/assets/faces/lm2/hate.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /><img src=\"/assets/faces/lm2/hate.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /><img src=\"/assets/faces/lm2/hate.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /><img src=\"/assets/faces/lm2/hate.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />"},{"pid":"d2fe46f5a3e12440499406d66ab5bf0f8132cdf9","tid":2279650,"uid":41658,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2020-11-10T02:41:39.000Z","msg":"<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/clown.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />"},{"pid":"deebf9473679668a7f2bd5748ce8a6f8f5f32ea8","tid":2279650,"uid":250105,"like":2,"dislike":0,"score":2,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2020-11-10T02:41:50.000Z","msg":"此回覆已被刪除"},{"pid":"86348fd6d870625faa5fdcc82c28b847794ad9ed","tid":2279650,"uid":228995,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":2,"replyTime":"2020-11-10T02:42:03.000Z","msg":"有無案底？長糧是否收皮了？"},{"pid":"713f2f6ab1ae6827da5fef05751136ca46b43610","tid":2279650,"uid":237425,"like":1,"dislike":0,"score":1,"citedBy":1,"replyTime":"2020-11-10T02:42:18.000Z","msg":"仲保到份工咁爽？<img src=\"/assets/faces/lm2/dead.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />"},{"pid":"07739d3795517cc899b4f4b97235e7495ee2c57f","tid":22796